What you need to know:  The Reds are in FA Cup action as they face Chelsea at Wembley at Saturday, offering City the chance to stretch their advantage to six points and further boost a seven-goal lead on goal difference.City have been in scintillating form since a 2-2 draw with Liverpool last month left the title race on a knife edge.Pep Guardiola's men have struck 22 goals in five games since to close in on a fourth title in five seasons.